    "metaDesc": "Learn about HVAC systems with Greenfoot Energy. Discover components, efficiency, and maintenance tips for your home's comfort.",
    "thumbnail": "/objects/blog-thumbnails/aab7130c-7d5c-43e2-96f8-313282360187.png",
    "thumbnailAlt": "Understanding HVAC Systems - Greenfoot Energy Solutions blog thumbnail",
