    "content": "<h1 id=>🌬️ HVAC &amp; Climate Control Services</h1><p>‍</p><p id=>At Greenfoot Energy Solutions, we believe in making homes and businesses smarter, more energy-efficient, and ultimately more comfortable. Whether you're battling extreme temperatures, planning to go solar, or simply looking to cut energy costs, our wide range of services has you covered. With a strong presence across Canada and a commitment to sustainability and innovation, Greenfoot is your one-stop solution for energy upgrades that actually make a difference.</p><ul id=><li id=><strong id=>Air Conditioning</strong><br>Stay cool and comfortable year-round with high-efficiency AC systems tailored to your space.</li><li id=><strong id=>Heat Pumps &amp; A/C</strong><br>Our heat pump solutions provide both heating and cooling, making them a smart and sustainable choice for your home or commercial property.</li><li id=><strong id=>Ducted-Central Heat Pumps</strong><br>For whole-home comfort and efficiency, we offer expertly designed ducted systems to evenly distribute temperature-controlled air.</li><li id=><strong id=>Mini-Split Heat Pumps</strong><br>Perfect for homes without existing ductwork, mini-splits offer customizable comfort in each room.</li><li id=><strong id=>Commercial HVAC</strong><br>Keep your business running smoothly with robust and scalable HVAC systems built for performance and reliability.</li></ul><h2 id=>🔋 Renewable &amp; Sustainable Energy</h2><ul id=><li id=><strong id=>Commercial Solar</strong><br>Offset your operational costs and carbon footprint with custom-designed solar energy systems for commercial buildings.</li><li id=><strong id=>Solar Energy</strong><br>Power your home with clean, renewable solar energy that reduces your utility bills and environmental impact.</li><li id=><strong id=>Geothermal Heat Pumps</strong><br>Tap into the earth’s natural energy for efficient heating and cooling with our state-of-the-art geothermal systems.</li></ul><h2 id=>🛠️ Insulation &amp; Energy Efficiency</h2><ul id=><li id=><strong id=>Sprayfoam Insulation</strong><br>Seal your home for ultimate energy savings. Sprayfoam blocks air leaks and increases structural integrity.</li><li id=><strong id=>Blown-In Insulation</strong><br>An excellent option for retrofitting existing homes, blown-in insulation improves comfort and efficiency.</li><li id=><strong id=>Batt &amp; Poly Insulation</strong><br>Cost-effective and reliable, batt insulation offers thermal and acoustic benefits for walls, attics, and more.</li><li id=><strong id=>Soundproofing</strong><br>Keep the peace—literally—with our expert soundproofing solutions for residential and commercial spaces.</li></ul><h2 id=>🔧 Maintenance, Monitoring &amp; Memberships</h2><ul id=><li id=><strong id=>Service &amp; Maintenance (Service Yeti)</strong><br>Our trusted technicians provide regular maintenance to keep your systems running at peak performance—powered by our Service Yeti platform.</li><li id=><strong id=>Remote Monitoring</strong><br>Keep tabs on your energy systems from anywhere with our smart monitoring solutions.</li><li id=><strong id=>Membership Plans</strong><br>Simplify your home maintenance with worry-free service packages that offer priority booking and discounts.</li></ul><h2 id=>🌡️ Air Quality, Controls &amp; More</h2><ul id=><li id=><strong id=>Indoor Air Quality</strong><br>Breathe easy with solutions that purify and balance indoor air, helping reduce allergens and improve overall wellness.</li><li id=><strong id=>Peak Thermostat</strong><br>Smart thermostats help you save money and energy by learning your schedule and adjusting automatically.</li><li id=><strong id=>Water Heaters</strong><br>From tankless to traditional, we install efficient water heaters to meet your household or commercial needs.</li><li id=><strong id=>Multi-Unit Appliances (Urban Yeti)</strong><br>Customized appliance solutions for high-density residential buildings and commercial spaces.</li><li id=><strong id=>Generators</strong><br>Don’t get left in the dark. Our backup generators ensure continuous power in any situation.</li></ul><h3 id=>Why Choose Greenfoot?</h3><p id=>We’re more than just another energy service provider. At Greenfoot Energy Solutions, we combine cutting-edge technology with personalized customer service to deliver energy systems that are built for real-world performance. We help our customers qualify for rebates, avoid costly mistakes, and choose the best solutions for their homes or businesses.</p><p id=><strong id=>Let’s Get Started</strong><br>Ready to upgrade your comfort and savings? Contact us today to book a free consultation or learn how much you could save with available government rebates.</p><p id=>‍</p><p id=>Joe Godbout</p><h4 id=>📞 1 (844) 725-4185<br>💻 Visit <a href=http://www.greenfootenergy.ca id=>greenfootenergy.ca</a></h4><p id=>‍</p>",
